snippet.title: NOVA LANDS – Release Date Trailer – Coming June 22
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1501610/Nova_Lands/

Explore a newfound planet and create your industry in this cozy automation base-building game coming to PC, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on June 22!
